            "content": [
              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Hi there! I'm here to assist you with a wide variety of topics, tasks, and questions. Here's just a sample of what I can do for you:\n\n### **Answering Questions**\n- Provide detailed answers to questions on general knowledge, science, history, technology, art, and more.\n- Definition, translations, or explanations of terms, concepts, or ideas.\n\n### **Productivity Tools**\n- Help you brainstorm ideas or draft essays, emails, or creative writing pieces.\n- Assist with organizing schedules, setting reminders, or creating to-do lists.\n- Solve math problems or analyze data.\n\n### **Learning**\n- Help you learn new subjects or skills step-by-step.\n- Explain hard concepts at different difficulty levels (from beginner to advanced).\n  \n### **Technical Help**\n- Troubleshoot issues with software, devices, or provide tech tutorials.\n- Write, debug, or explain code in various programming languages.\n\n### **Creative Fun**\n- Assist with writing poems, jokes, story prompts, or design ideas.\n- Play word games or collaborate on creative projects.\n\n### **Decision Making**\n- Help you weigh pros and cons or brainstorm solutions.\n- Provide insights into choices related to your projects, career, or personal dilemmas.\n\nIf you have something specific in mind, let me know, and I'll do my best to assist! \uD83D\uDE0A",
